type sequence
title Codex drives the app with Chrome DevTools MCP to validate its work

participant CODEX { fill: dotgrid }
participant APP { fill: none }
participant "CHROME DEVTOOLS" { fill: crosshatch }

CODEX -> APP: Select target + clear console
CODEX -> CHROME_DEVTOOLS: Snapshot **BEFORE**
CODEX -> APP: Trigger UI path
APP -> CHROME_DEVTOOLS: Runtime events | (during interaction)
CODEX -> CHROME_DEVTOOLS: Snapshot **AFTER**
CODEX -> APP: Apply fix + restart

loop UNTIL CLEAN
  CODEX -> CHROME_DEVTOOLS: Re-run validation
end
